Files explanation

minion.py:
- Main interface for every minion. The methods in this class will be the ones used by any external software (relative to the minion).

lc_minion.py:
- Minion that uses LibCloud to connect to other providers. It implements minion.py interface. Also, if executed on separate process (python lc_minion.py &) it creates a listening RPC process that can be called from ZeroRPC library.

openstack.js:
- Node.js module that test RPC capability of a remote RPC minion.

test.py:
- File used to for testing of minions from python.

ref folder:
- Contains useful tests scripts to configure VMs instances.
